==English==

===Verb===
'''sparkling'''

# [[Present participle]] of '''to [[sparkle]]'''

===Adjective===
'''sparkling''' (''no {{compar}} or {{superl}}'')

# Of an object, reflecting light as if giving off tiny sparks.
# Of a [[beverage]], especially an [[alcoholic]] beverage, containing [[dissolve]]d [[carbon dioxide]] (either naturally or that has been added) that comes out of [[solution]] in the form of many tiny [[bubble]]s.

====Synonyms====

*(''of an object, reflecting light''): [[glisten]]ing, [[twinkle|twinkling]]
*(''of a beverage''): [[fizzy]]

